org.apache.juneau.rest.debug

Class BasicDebugEnablement

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.rest.debug.DebugEnablement
      • org.apache.juneau.rest.debug.BasicDebugEnablement

  • public class BasicDebugEnablement
extends DebugEnablement
    Default implementation of the DebugEnablement interface.

    Enables debug mode based on the following annotations:

    • Rest.debug()
    • RestOp.debug()
    • Rest.debugOn()
    • Overview > juneau-rest-server > Logging / Debugging
